{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1783488439722,"sessionID":"ses_0bfd0e5b8ffeU7MvrL6T6jXOre","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_cbe1733eca5f4034b542f2e4","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-2/synthesis-v1.md"},"output":"<path>/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-2/synthesis-v1.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # Synthesis Snapshot v1\n2: \n3: Canonical synthesis lives in `research.md`.\n4: \n5: Stop reason: `converged` after 5 iterations. Top corrections: fan-out spec-writeback boundary, artifact-root path seam, broader reverse-coupling inventory, advisor re-baseline discipline, and cautious GLM to MiMo fallback wiring.\n\n(End of file - total 5 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# Synthesis Snapshot v1\n\nCanonical synthesis lives in `research.md`.\n\nStop reason: `converged` after 5 iterations. Top corrections: fan-out spec-writeback boundary, artifact-root path seam, broader reverse-coupling inventory, advisor re-baseline discipline, and cautious GLM to MiMo fallback wiring.","truncated":false,"loaded":[],"display":{"type":"file","path":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-2/synthesis-v1.md","text":"# Synthesis Snapshot v1\n\nCanonical synthesis lives in `research.md`.\n\nStop reason: `converged` after 5 iterations. Top corrections: fan-out spec-writeback boundary, artifact-root path seam, broader reverse-coupling inventory, advisor re-baseline discipline, and cautious GLM to MiMo fallback wiring.","lineStart":1,"lineEnd":5,"totalLines":5,"truncated":false}},"title":".opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-2/synthesis-v1.md","time":{"start":1783488439708,"end":1783488439720}},"id":"prt_f4031e59a001Gi24wmOx1PCcYK","sessionID":"ses_0bfd0e5b8ffeU7MvrL6T6jXOre","messageID":"msg_f4031c7a8001zInZ2gjcYhZAqE"}}
